What is CPO Switch?
CPO (Co-Packaged Optics) switches are revolutionizing high-speed data communication in North America by integrating optical transceivers, lasers, and photonics elements directly alongside switch silicon on the same substrate. This approach overcomes limitations of traditional pluggable optics, minimizing signal loss, power usage, and latency while boosting bandwidth density for hyperscale environments.
